``` python
from nilearn import datasets
from nilearn._utils.numpy_conversions import csv_to_array

atl = datasets.fetch_atlas_msdl()
csv_to_array(atl.labels) # nans

csv_to_array(atl.labels, dtype=None) # no nans
```

I am not sure whether it is an issue or upto user to use `dtype=None`
title: nan values are returned by csv_to_array
nan values are returned by csv_to_array
